#. type: Plain text
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:434
msgid ""
"Since the password is not echoed when typed, be careful to not mistype the "
"password when creating the user account."
msgstr "由于输入密码时没有回显，所以在创建用户账户时要注意不要打错密码。"

#. type: Title ====
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:437
#, no-wrap
msgid "`rmuser`"
msgstr "`rmuser`"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:441
msgid ""
"To completely remove a user from the system, run man:rmuser[8] as the "
"superuser.  This command performs the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"要从系统中完全删除一个用户，请以超级用户身份运行 rmuser[8] 。该命令执行以下步骤："

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:444
msgid "Removes the user's man:crontab[1] entry, if one exists."
msgstr "删除用户的 man:crontab[1] 条目，如果存在的话。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:445
msgid "Removes any man:at[1] jobs belonging to the user."
msgstr "删除属于该用户的任何 man:at[1] 作业。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:446
msgid "Kills all processes owned by the user."
msgstr "杀死所有属于该用户的进程。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:447
msgid "Removes the user from the system's local password file."
msgstr "从系统的本地密码文件中删除该用户。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:448
msgid "Optionally removes the user's home directory, if it is owned by the user."
msgstr "可以选择删除用户的主目录，如果该目录是由用户拥有的话。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:449
msgid ""
"Removes the incoming mail files belonging to the user from [.filename]#/var/"
"mail#."
msgstr "从 [.filename]#/var/mail# 中删除属于该用户的接收邮件文件。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:450
msgid ""
"Removes all files owned by the user from temporary file storage areas such as [."
"filename]#/tmp#."
msgstr "从临时文件存储区（如 [.filename]#/tmp# ）中删除属于该用户的所有文件。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:451
msgid ""
"Finally, removes the username from all groups to which it belongs in [."
"filename]#/etc/group#. If a group becomes empty and the group name is the same "
"as the username, the group is removed. This complements the per-user unique "
"groups created by man:adduser[8]."
msgstr ""
"最后，从 [.filename]#/etc/group# 中所有属于该用户的组中删除该用户。如果一个组变成"
"空的，并且组名与用户名相同，那么这个组就会被删除。这补充了由 man:adduser[8] 创建"
"的每个用户的唯一组。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:453
msgid ""
"man:rmuser[8] cannot be used to remove superuser accounts since that is almost "
"always an indication of massive destruction."
msgstr "man:rmuser[8] 不能用来删除超级用户账户，因为这几乎是大规模破坏的表现。"

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:455
msgid "By default, an interactive mode is used, as shown in the following example."
msgstr "默认情况下，使用的是交互式模式，如下面的例子所示。"

#. type: Block title
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:456
#, no-wrap
msgid "`rmuser` Interactive Account Removal"
msgstr "`rmuser` 交互式账户的删除"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: content/zh-cn/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:468
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# rmuser jru\n"
"Matching password entry:\n"
"jru:*:1001:1001::0:0:J. Random User:/home/jru:/usr/local/bin/zsh\n"
"Is this the entry you wish to remove? y\n"
"Remove user's home directory (/home/jru)? y\n"
"Removing user (jru): mailspool home passwd.\n"
"#\n"
msgstr ""
"# rmuser jru\n"
"Matching password entry:\n"
"jru:*:1001:1001::0:0:J. Random User:/home/jru:/usr/local/bin/zsh\n"
"Is this the entry you wish to remove? y\n"
"Remove user's home directory (/home/jru)? y\n"
"Removing user (jru): mailspool home passwd.\n"
"#\n"

#. type: Title ====
